---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "ASAOSA - Valorización de Residuos"
description: "ONG dedicada a la valorización de residuos mediante reciclaje y compostaje. Aprende qué materiales
aceptamos y cómo preparar tus residuos para el centro de acopio."
---

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden pt-20" id="inicio">
  <!-- Video Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden brightness-[.5]">
    <iframe
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/i7LGcgGXxyM?autoplay=1&mute=1&controls=0&loop=1&playlist=i7LGcgGXxyM&modestbranding=1&rel=0&showinfo=0&playsinline=1&disablekb=1&iv_load_policy=3"
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[177.78vh] min-w-full h-full min-h-[56.25vw] pointer-events-none object-cover"
      frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen loading="lazy" title="Video de fondo - Reciclaje"></iframe>
  </div>
  <!-- Overlay oscuro para mejorar legibilidad del texto -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[rgba(45,80,22,0.75)] to-[rgba(74,124,47,0.7)] z-[1]"></div>
  <!-- Contenido del hero -->
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 py-16 text-center relative z-[10]">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-2xl">Transformamos
      Residuos en Valor</h1>
    <p class="text-white text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 drop-shadow-lg">
      Juntos creamos un futuro más sostenible a través del reciclaje y la
      valorización de residuos. Cada material que reciclas hace la
      diferencia.
    </p>
    <a href="#materiales"
      title="Ver los materiales que reciclamos en ASAOSA"
      class="inline-block rounded-full px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4 lg:px-10 lg:py-4 text-white bg-accent hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-all duration-300 text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-[22px] font-bold shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95 border-b-4 border-yellow-700">
      Descubre Qué Reciclamos
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MATERIALS SECTION -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12" id="materiales">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Materiales</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">¿Qué Materiales Reciclamos?</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Aceptamos una amplia variedad de materiales valorizables. Encuentra el tuyo y comienza a reciclar.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      {% for material in materiales %}
      <div
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="{{ loop.index0 * 100 }}"
        class="material-card group bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-green-50 dark:bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <span class="material-icons-outlined text-3xl text-primary">{{ material.icono }}</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">{{ material.nombre }}</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">{{ material.descripcion }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ROUTES SECTION -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12" id="rutas">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Calendario de Recolección</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-3 mb-4">Nuestras Rutas</h2>
    <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-8"></div>
    <p class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg">
      Sigue nuestro cronograma mensual para saber cuándo pasaremos por tu comunidad.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="absolute top-16 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 hidden lg:block"></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-x-4 gap-y-12 lg:gap-6 lg:justify-between">
      {% for ruta in rutas %}
      <div 
        data-aos="zoom-in"
        data-aos-delay="{{ loop.index0 * 100 }}"
        class="flex flex-col items-center relative h-full">
        <div
          class="relative z-10 w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark border-4 border-primary shadow-timeline flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300 mb-6 md:mb-10 group">
          <span class="text-[10px] md:text-sm sm:text-xs uppercase font-bold text-gray-400 text-primary">{{ ruta.frecuencia }}</span>
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">{{ ruta.dia }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if not loop.last %}
        <div class="absolute top-32 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-0.5 h-10 bg-gray-100 lg:hidden"></div>
        {% endif %}
        <div
          class="m-2 w-full flex-1 bg-background-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all text-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4 block text-3xl md:text-4xl">location_on</span>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-base md:text-lg mb-4">Puntos de Entrega</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 md:space-y-3">
            {% for punto in ruta.puntos %}
            <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm md:text-base">
              <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span> {{ punto }}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PLASTICS SECTION -->
<section class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark py-12" id="plasticos">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Tipos de Plásticos Reciclables</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Conoce los plásticos que aceptamos y aprende a identificarlos por su código de reciclaje.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      {% for plastico in plasticos %}
      <div
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="{{ loop.index0 * 150 }}"
        class="plastic-card bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col items-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div
          class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold mb-4 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30">
          {{ plastico.numero }}</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{{ plastico.sigla }}</h3>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4">{{ plastico.nombre }}</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center mb-6 text-sm">{{ plastico.descripcion }}</p>
        <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-background-dark w-full rounded-md p-5">
          <p class="font-bold text-sm text-primary mb-3">Ejemplos comunes:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            {% for ejemplo in plastico.ejemplos %}
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary">check_circle</span>{{ ejemplo }}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 bg-[#EFF6E8] dark:bg-primary/20 rounded-md p-6 flex items-start gap-4 shadow-md">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-green-600">emoji_objects</span>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Consejo Importante</h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Busca el número dentro del símbolo de reciclaje (triángulo de flechas) en la parte inferior de los envases. Si
          es #1 (PET) o #2 (HDPE), ¡lo aceptamos! Otros números de plástico actualmente no los procesamos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PREPARATION SECTION -->
<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden py-12" id="preparacion">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Preparación</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">¿Cómo Preparar Tus Residuos?</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Sigue estos pasos simples para asegurar que tus materiales sean aceptados en nuestro centro de acopio.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {% for paso in preparacion %}
      <div
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-delay="{{ loop.index0 * 100 }}"
        class="step flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 p-6 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-l-8 hover:border-l-secondary transition-all">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold text-xl">
            {{ loop.index }}</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">{{ paso.titulo }}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {{ paso.descripcion }}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
